OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scottish Parliament staff are no longer
OL,6, allowed to wear rainbow lanyards - or  
OL,7, other accessories that show support for
OL,8, social movements - at Holyrood.        
OL,10,FAll staff must now wear a generic      
OL,11,Fpurple lanyard with immediate effect.  
OL,13,FClaire Baker, an MSP who sits on the   
OL,14,FScottish Parliament's Corporate Body   
OL,15,F(SPCB), announced the changes in the   
OL,16,FHolyrood chamber earlier.              
OL,18,FA parliament spokesperson said: "This  
OL,19,Fdecision will help minimise the risk of
OL,20,Fperceived bias."                       
